### Create an order
POST http://localhost:3000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prodId": "{{productId}}",  # Replace after getting a product ID
  "qty": 2,
  "email": "customer@example.com"
}

### Update order status
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/orders/{{orderId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 1
}